snippet.title: Announcement Trailer - Unfortunate Spacemen
snippet.description:
Unfortunate Spacemen is a multiplayer game about space-based murder in space! Spacemen work diligently to be rescued from their failing outpost, but not everyone is who they claim to be...

Coming to Steam Early Access - May 6th, 2016

Stay tuned for more info!
http://unfortunate.space

Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/UnfortSpacemen
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/UnfortunateSpacemen
Reddit: http://www.reddit.com/r/UnfortunateSpacemen

Music Credit: Ross Bugden (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQKG...)

Current Development Stage: PRE-ALPHA
Everything you see here is absolutely a work in progress and is in no way final.

Powered by Unreal Engine 4
